"Soon as I get this fellow settled in," Wheeljack acknowledges, 
hooking Blackfang up to a diagnostic/life-support machine.  He 
doesn't want to risk using the CR with his comrade in such a 
condition.  As an afterthought, he takes out a datapad and enters a 
small note: "This Maximal is in a coma; computer will give alert if 
anything changes."

Leaving the note by Blackfang's bedside, he dashes through the halls, 
homing in on Rodimus.  Catching up, Jackie taps him on the shoulder.  
"Tag, you're it!"
